CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 6, 1956, pg. A9 reads: "Opening Of Thee Doors - The formal opening of the doors of the new home of the Council of Churches of the Pittsburgh Area occurred this week. Pictured are Dr. Ernest V. Mays, left , discussing the program outline with the Rev. James B. Cayce, center, and the Rev. Donald P. Brickley of the First Church of the Nazarene, Mount Washington, right.  The Rev. Mr. Cayce is president of the Protestant Ministers Union. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Dr. Ernest V. Mays, Rev. James B. Cayce, and Rev. Donald P. Brickley, discussing opening of Council of Churches
